AddressInfo.AccessComments:
The location is called "Conacul Archia" and can be found on all maps: Google Maps, Waze, etc

Conacul Archia is an 1920 Mansion with 19 thematic rooms, 2 villas, equestrian center, outside swimming pool and an a la carte restaurant. 

Conacul Archia is located 3km (2.1 miles) from Deva city in the village with beautiful surroundings. 

The reception of the mansion is opened 24/7. 

The a la carte restaurant “Restaurant CAROL” is opened daily from 12:30 - 23:00 with the last order being at 22:30. It serves Romanian, Hungarian and International dishes.
